                <mxCell id="25" value="2. Output will always be same for same input text/file, even single bit change/replacement will change the output completely, this is called &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 101, 255));&quot;&gt;Avalanche effect&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="10">
